en_383236_0	An educative programme on ‘Human Rights’ was conducted on Monday (25) in the Security Force Headquarters - Wanni (SFHQ-W) premises for troops of under-command formations.
en_383236_1	The lecture also touched on issues, related to fundamental rights.
en_383236_2	Major General Kumudu Perera, Commander, Security Forces - Wanni on Monday (25), initiated the project.
en_383236_3	Coordinating Officer in the Human Rights Commission in Vavuniya, Mr. M R Priyadharshana and Regional Coordinating Officer of the Human Rights Commission in Anuradhapura, Mrs Shiromi Priyanga delivered those informative lectures.
en_383236_4	More than 25 Officers and 300 Other Ranks attended the lecture.
